ðŸ“Š Grafana Dashboard
Import Dashboard

Open Grafana â†’ http://localhost:3001 (admin / admin).

Go to Dashboards â†’ Import.

Paste the JSON below in â€œImport via panel jsonâ€.

Select InfluxDB datasource when asked.

JSON FILE:
  {
  "id": null,
  "title": "IoT Realtime Dashboard",
  "timezone": "browser",
  "schemaVersion": 36,
  "version": 1,
  "refresh": "5s",
  "panels": [
